{{Quote|This is Kornova Corp expedition IL5 calling for help &hellip; We are in desperate need of medical supplies &hellip; Any ship in the area please respond &hellip; Coordinates follow &hellip;|Distress call sent by expedition IL5|<ref name="The Entity (adventure)">{{WEGCite|story=The Entity (adventure)|book=Star Wars Gamemaster Screen}}</ref>}}
'''Expedition IL5 ''' was a group of [[Scientist/Legends|scientists]] and [[Archaeologist/Legends|archaeologists]] working for the [[Kornova Corp]], excavating ancient ruins of an unknown [[Species/Legends|species]] underneath a glacier. When they broke into a new level of the ruins, they released a dangerous [[Bio-engineered assassin|entity]] that began preying on expedition members. A cunning creature bio-engineered by the ancient species as a perfect [[Assassin/Legends|assassin]], it managed to disable IL5's [[Starship/Legends|starship]] and most of their communication equipment. Expedition IL5 managed to cobble together a weak broadcasting unit, and sent out a distress call.

